trans-unit.source: Provides the stack functionality for a stack of server response channel sinks.
trans-unit.target: 提供的服务器响应通道堆栈的堆栈功能接收器。

trans-unit.source: Requests asynchronous processing of a method call on the sinks in the current sink stack.
trans-unit.target: 在当前的接收器堆栈中接收器调用异步方法的处理的请求。

trans-unit.source: The AsyncProcessResponse method initializes asynchronous processing on the top sink in the current sink stack.
trans-unit.target: AsyncProcessResponse 方法会初始化当前的接收器堆栈的顶部接收器上的异步处理。

trans-unit.source: For additional information, see the <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IServerChannelSink.AsyncProcessResponse%2A> method.
